SANTO seat by SII Deutschland won the Passenger Comfort Hardware award at The Crystal Cabin Awards in Hamburg . 
  It is one-and-a-half times the width of a standard seat and makes use of wasted space at the back of aircraft . 
  The chair is ideal for obese passengers and small children . 
  It beat off competition from 21 finalists to win the award at the Aircraft Interiors Expo . 
 